### ADMIN-ONLY ENDPOINTS
### ================================

### 31. Get Dashboard Stats (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 32. Get All Users (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 33. Deactivate User (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/user_id_here/deactivate
